            <section>
                <div class="topic zr-gray-bg">
                    <div class="topic-chunk">
                        <div class="image">
                            <img alt="several kids are gathered in a manger scene" src="https://zionsrefugechurch.com/images/photo_4911440904687037676_y.jpg">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="topic-chunk">
                        <div class="topic-heading">
                            <h3>Kids</h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="topic-chunk">
                        <div class="text">
                            <p>Kids from 3 to 12 years of age get to learn about the amazing true stories of
                                the Bible in three age-appropriate classrooms. Our teachers provide a safe
                                environment of love and appreciation where each child is able to learn about
                                the Love of God.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="topic zr-gray-bg">
                    <div class="topic-chunk">
                        <div class="image">
                            <img alt="pastor David Parsons poses with a church youth member" src="../img/pastor-teen.jpg">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="topic-chunk">
                        <div class="topic-heading">
                            <h3>Teens</h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="topic-chunk">
                        <div class="text">
                            <p>Teens 13-17 are challenged to move up and learn how to carry the Gospel to
                                the ends of earth. The teachers provide a safe environment that encourages
                                teens to ask questions, seek wisdom, and actively serve God.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="topic zr-gray-bg">
                    <div class="topic-chunk">
                        <div class="image">
                            <img alt="three adults are gathered near a fire playing instruments and laughing" src="../img/adults-fun.jpg">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="topic-chunk">
                        <div class="topic-heading">
                            <h3>Adults</h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="topic-chunk">
                        <div class="text">
                            <p>Adults have two classes. One is a lecture style classroom and the other is
                                more conversational. Both classes provide a safe environment to grow in
                                grace and wisdom as we discuss biblical concepts, philosophy, and current
                                events.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
